00:30:46,140 --> 00:30:48,660
 Ja rekao, prijatelj, danas počne tvoj uspon.

1028
00:30:48,660 --> 00:30:51,360
 Danas počne tek kad si ti priznao da si slab.

1029
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:54,240
 Kako je važno priznati

1030
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:56,420
 znak duhovne zrelosti

1031
00:30:56,420 --> 00:30:58,900
 i znači priznati da ne možeš,

1032
00:30:58,900 --> 00:31:00,200
 ne možeš čovječe.

1033
00:31:00,200 --> 00:31:01,140
 Slab si.

1034
00:31:01,140 --> 00:31:03,820
 Petar je dokaz tome.

1035
00:31:04,980 --> 00:31:07,320
 I taj isti Petar u Getsemani,

1036
00:31:07,320 --> 00:31:09,460
 isti Petar u Getsemani,

1037
00:31:09,460 --> 00:31:11,720
 on ne može i uzima mač.

1038
00:31:11,720 --> 00:31:12,940
 Uzima mač.

1039
00:31:12,940 --> 00:31:14,280
 I on hoće se boriti.

1040
00:31:14,280 --> 00:31:16,480
 I on ide svojim silema

1041
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:19,000
 i pogodi onoga sluge velikog sveđa

1042
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:20,320
 da ga je, Bože mi ja prosti,

1043
00:31:20,320 --> 00:31:21,360
 bar pogodio kako treba.

1044
00:31:21,360 --> 00:31:24,460
 Nego s ona uko čovječe.

1045
00:31:24,460 --> 00:31:28,220
 Bože, sačuje.

1046
00:31:28,220 --> 00:31:29,900
 Pa je.

1047
00:31:29,900 --> 00:31:32,180
 Da ga je, bar pogodio kako treba.

1048
00:31:34,180 --> 00:31:35,100
 Bože, sačuje.

1049
00:31:35,100 --> 00:31:39,380
 E, a taj isti Petar,

1050
00:31:39,380 --> 00:31:41,480
 tu noć,

1051
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:44,220
 sat, dva, tri prije,

1052
00:31:44,220 --> 00:31:47,100
 odnosno kasnije,

1053
00:31:47,100 --> 00:31:49,280
 ta ista faca koja je rekao

1054
00:31:49,280 --> 00:31:51,000
 ja ću umrijeti za tebe, Isuse,

1055
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:52,020
 umrijet ću za tebe.

1056
00:31:52,020 --> 00:31:56,620
 Jedna sluškinja, djevojčica,

1057
00:31:56,620 --> 00:31:58,580
 najvratnije je bila ropkinja nečija.

1058
00:31:58,580 --> 00:32:02,660
 I primijetila ga da je Galilejac po naglasku.

1059
00:32:03,380 --> 00:32:05,500
 I ona je rekao, zar si ti?

1060
00:32:05,500 --> 00:32:08,520
 Dakle, jedna mala djevojčica jednom Petru kaže,

1061
00:32:08,520 --> 00:32:09,060
 bu.

1062
00:32:09,060 --> 00:32:11,000
 I on, bu, skočio.

1063
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:13,240
 Je, bu.

1064
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:15,520
 I on skočio.

1065
00:32:15,520 --> 00:32:18,860
 I pogledaj šta Petar radi u ovoj fazi.

1066
00:32:18,860 --> 00:32:21,760
 Što je posljedna na mnogi od nas.

1067
00:32:21,760 --> 00:32:25,340
 I ovo je slika tipičnog kršćanina.

1068
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:28,020
 Blizak je Isusa.

1069
00:32:28,020 --> 00:32:30,500
 Ipak moramo priznati da Petar nije napustio Isusa.

1070
00:32:30,500 --> 00:32:33,000
 Ipak je slijedio iz daleka,

1071
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:34,580
 da ga ima na oko,

1072
00:32:34,580 --> 00:32:36,760
 ali dovojno daleko da nije njegov.

1073
00:32:36,760 --> 00:32:38,620
 Tu smo.

1074
00:32:38,620 --> 00:32:41,760
 Hrvat katolik.

1075
00:32:44,460 --> 00:32:45,260
 Jesam njegov,

1076
00:32:45,260 --> 00:32:47,480
 ali dovojno distancirano,

1077
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:51,340
 da ne bi bilo opasnost da me povežu s njim,

1078
00:32:51,340 --> 00:32:52,920
 ali ga ipak slijedim.

1079
00:32:52,920 --> 00:32:54,240
 Jer ne možu reći da ga ne slijedi,

1080
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:55,780
 ali na kakav način.

1081
00:32:58,980 --> 00:33:00,040
 Grije se kod vatre.

1082
00:33:00,040 --> 00:33:03,940
 Vrlo jedno komotno kršćanstvo.

1083
00:33:03,940 --> 00:33:08,760
 Vrlo jedno komfortno kršćanstvo.

1084
00:33:08,760 --> 00:33:11,220
 Je, je, ja, slijedim Isusa.

1085
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:12,160
 Eno ga tamo.

1086
00:33:12,160 --> 00:33:16,840
 Ali neću se ja identificirati s njim.

1087
00:33:16,840 --> 00:33:19,480
 I usput grijem se kod...

1088
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:23,820
 Ono grijanje kod vatre je biser evanđovski.

1089
00:33:23,820 --> 00:33:27,940
 Što prokazuje sve nas.

1090
00:33:28,980 --> 00:33:33,360
 Kako kršćanstvo ponekad za nas je jedan konfor,

1091
00:33:33,360 --> 00:33:34,420
 jedan nakit.

1092
00:33:34,420 --> 00:33:36,400
 Grijanje kod vatre.

1093
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:37,880
 A ovaj tamo daje život.

1094
00:33:37,880 --> 00:33:42,160
 Ovo mene uvijek potresi.

1095
00:33:42,160 --> 00:33:44,040
 Jer se ja često tu vidim.

1096
00:33:44,040 --> 00:33:46,740
 Često se tu vidim.

1097
00:33:46,740 --> 00:33:49,600
 Gdje jesam njegov, ali nisam njegov.

1098
00:33:49,600 --> 00:33:52,160
 Slijedim ga, ali dovoljno daleko,

1099
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,800
 dovoljno blizu i grijem se usput.

1100
00:33:53,800 --> 00:33:56,740
 Duhovna slabost.

1101
00:33:58,340 --> 00:33:59,540
 Duhovna slabost.

1102
00:33:59,540 --> 00:34:05,560
 I također duhovni neuspjeh.

1103
00:34:05,560 --> 00:34:09,920
 Svi se toga bojimo.

1104
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:13,420
 Ja to slušam svaki dan u ispovedonici.

1105
00:34:13,420 --> 00:34:16,160
 Meni je najtežak da mi svećinici dođu.

1106
00:34:16,160 --> 00:34:18,260
 Koji dignu ruke.

1107
00:34:18,260 --> 00:34:20,440
 Koji ne mogu više.

1108
00:34:22,180 --> 00:34:25,480
 Ja isto sam, koliko duhovne neuspjehe ja doživim.

1109
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:29,280
 Znate, koliko duhovne neuspjehe ja doživim.

1110
00:34:29,280 --> 00:34:32,200
 Razočaranje.

1111
00:34:32,200 --> 00:34:41,400
 Petar je tako doživio upravo u dvorištu velikog svećnika.

1112
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:44,640
 Koji duhovni neuspjeh zatajio Isusa.

1113
00:34:44,640 --> 00:34:47,440
 Ja želim da znate jednu stvar.

1114
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:51,080
 Posobno oni koji su u službu evangelizacije.

1115
00:34:53,080 --> 00:34:58,220
 Ti kad evangeliziraš, gospodin je gospodar žetve, ne ti.

1116
00:34:58,220 --> 00:35:00,580
 Ja znam da želimo plodove.

1117
00:35:00,580 --> 00:35:02,980
 Ali nekad ćete biti uskraćeni plodove.

1118
00:35:02,980 --> 00:35:11,980
 I evanđovska statistika je da 70% tvoje evangelizacije neće uroditi nikakvog ploda.

1119
00:35:11,980 --> 00:35:13,920
 To je onaj sijač koji sije.

1120
00:35:13,920 --> 00:35:16,540
 I to je najrazrađenija prispodoba.

1121
00:35:16,540 --> 00:35:19,120
 Toliko da ne bi bilo sumnje Isus nam daje tumačenje.

1122
00:35:19,460 --> 00:35:23,760
 Neke sjeme pada na trnovito plod u drači.

1123
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:24,900
 Ne znam što već u trnje.

1124
00:35:24,900 --> 00:35:25,740
 I tako.

1125
00:35:25,740 --> 00:35:28,120
 I 25% pada na dobro tlo.

1126
00:35:28,120 --> 00:35:30,800
 Dakle, ja to družim seminar za svećnike.

1127
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:32,380
 Ja to njima kažem.

1128
00:35:32,380 --> 00:35:34,680
 Braću svećnici, nemaš pravo na ploda.

1129
00:35:34,680 --> 00:35:35,420
 Nemaš pravo.

1130
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:38,720
 Čak ja bih rekao u onom neuspjehu.

1131
00:35:38,720 --> 00:35:43,980
 Ali u poniznom radu gospodin je gospodar žetve.

1132
00:35:43,980 --> 00:35:44,700
 Zašto?

1133
00:35:44,700 --> 00:35:47,940
 Jer kod Petra uspon njegov počinje

1134
00:35:47,940 --> 00:35:51,000
 kad je doživio najveći poraz.

1135
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:52,000
 Kad je za taj Isus.

1136
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:52,400
 Zašto?

1137
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:56,480
 Jer je pogledao Isusa i gorko zaplako.

1138
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,760
 Opet ono kajanje.

1139
00:35:57,760 --> 00:36:01,640
 Zato u toj fazi pročišćenje

1140
00:36:01,640 --> 00:36:04,500
