1141
00:36:04,500 --> 00:36:07,260
 opet ima oko na Isusa.

1142
00:36:07,260 --> 00:36:08,440
 I to je tako važno.

1143
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:09,640
 Tako je to važno.

1144
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:12,920
 Druga faza.

1145
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:13,840
 Prva faza je najduža.

1146
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:14,280
 Ne bojte se.

1147
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:18,340
 Druga faza je put prosvjetljenje.

1148
00:36:18,340 --> 00:36:21,060
 I nekako kod Petra, to se vidi kod Petra

1149
00:36:21,060 --> 00:36:25,400
 od Kristovog uskrasnuće do pedesetnice.

1150
00:36:25,400 --> 00:36:28,980
 I sad, ti 40 dana su možda,

1151
00:36:28,980 --> 00:36:33,140
 40 dana, toa faza biblijska je možda

1152
00:36:33,140 --> 00:36:37,500
 najnecijenjenije razdoblje Biblije.

1153
00:36:37,500 --> 00:36:37,900
 Zašto?

1154
00:36:37,900 --> 00:36:39,840
 Jer svi znamo, ok, ajmo duhove,

1155
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:41,680
 idemo, o, 50 dana, idemo.

1156
00:36:41,680 --> 00:36:47,060
 Ali ja također vidim nas Hrvate, katolike,

1157
00:36:47,060 --> 00:36:48,980
 kršćane Evrope, pogotovo,

1158
00:36:48,980 --> 00:36:54,700
 u trajnom stanju između uskrsnuća i pedesetnice.

1159
00:36:54,700 --> 00:36:56,260
 Zašto?

1160
00:36:56,260 --> 00:37:00,080
 Zato što mi znamo da je on uskrsnu,

1161
00:37:00,080 --> 00:37:02,620
 mi znamo sve, ali nikako da krene.

1162
00:37:04,580 --> 00:37:06,200
 Ja sam rekao na dva učenika,

1163
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:09,000
 prema Emosu, to su tipični Hrvati.

1164
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:12,560
 Sve znaju, a idu u krivi smjer.

1165
00:37:12,560 --> 00:37:14,900
 Pa živa istina.

1166
00:37:14,900 --> 00:37:18,960
 Ja pijem kavo svaku, kad sam u uredu na Cvjetnom,

1167
00:37:18,960 --> 00:37:21,280
 ima jedan kafić preko tamo, 12 godina,

1168
00:37:21,280 --> 00:37:22,400
 znam svakoga tamo.

1169
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:24,540
 I iste face svaki dan,

1170
00:37:24,540 --> 00:37:26,480
 samo se spuste iz grade dolje.

1171
00:37:26,480 --> 00:37:29,420
 Ja ti košanka samo jedan espresso,

1172
00:37:29,420 --> 00:37:31,000
 popijem i idem dalje,

1173
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:33,520
 ali dovojno da ja načujem priču.

1174
00:37:33,580 --> 00:37:35,320
 Znači, ti tamo dođeš

1175
00:37:35,320 --> 00:37:37,040
 i to ljudi znaju,

1176
00:37:37,040 --> 00:37:38,640
 ma kakav Dalić,

1177
00:37:38,640 --> 00:37:39,800
 ma treba izbornik Hrvatske.

1178
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:41,100
 Rat u Siriji.

1179
00:37:41,100 --> 00:37:42,840
 Pa ovi su riješili to sve.

1180
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:44,760
 Znači, sve živo znaju.

1181
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:46,880
 Sve znaju.

1182
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:48,140
 Nema, to u čovječe.

1183
00:37:48,140 --> 00:37:50,260
 Ja pokupim te priče od nje.

1184
00:37:50,260 --> 00:37:51,000
 Sve znaju.

1185
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:56,180
 Dakle, ova faza,

1186
00:37:56,180 --> 00:37:57,660
 40 dana,

1187
00:37:57,660 --> 00:37:59,480
 oni znaju,

1188
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:03,560
 ali još ne dopire do njih.

1189
00:38:03,580 --> 00:38:05,220
 i to je većina katolika.

1190
00:38:05,220 --> 00:38:07,080
 Većina katolika.

1191
00:38:07,080 --> 00:38:08,260
 Ok.

1192
00:38:08,260 --> 00:38:10,280
 Ovdje Peter doživljava

1193
00:38:10,280 --> 00:38:11,820
 njegovo drugo obraćenje.

1194
00:38:11,820 --> 00:38:12,500
 Ok.

1195
00:38:12,500 --> 00:38:14,060
 Isus njega rehabilitira.

1196
00:38:14,060 --> 00:38:14,260
 Vići?

1197
00:38:14,260 --> 00:38:16,400
 I Peter doživa još jedno obraćenje

1198
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:18,140
 u toj fazi prosvjetljenja.

1199
00:38:18,140 --> 00:38:20,420
 Dakle,

1200
00:38:20,420 --> 00:38:23,400
 šta se tu događa?

1201
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:25,320
 Peter ga,

1202
00:38:25,320 --> 00:38:26,880
 Isus ga tri put ponovno pita.

1203
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:28,140
 Peter, sine,

1204
00:38:28,140 --> 00:38:28,780
 Šimono,

1205
00:38:28,780 --> 00:38:30,680
 ljubiš li me?

1206
00:38:30,680 --> 00:38:31,960
 Ljubiš li me?

1207
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:32,600
 Ljubiš li me?

1208
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:33,100
 Tri puta.

1209
00:38:33,100 --> 00:38:33,840
 Ok.

1210
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:35,380
 Ovaj prevod je jako zanimljiv.

1211
00:38:35,380 --> 00:38:35,600
 Ok.

1212
00:38:35,600 --> 00:38:36,880
 Ok.

1213
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:38,080
 Imam ja jedan program doma.

1214
00:38:38,080 --> 00:38:39,260
 To je tako zanimljivo.

1215
00:38:39,260 --> 00:38:40,100
 Ja, mislim,

1216
00:38:40,100 --> 00:38:41,300
 možete svi misli da sam ja luda.

1217
00:38:41,300 --> 00:38:42,380
 Ja kada imam slobodno vrijeme.

1218
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:44,380
 Dakle, upališ taj program.

1219
00:38:44,380 --> 00:38:45,360
 Mislim, upravo.

1220
00:38:45,360 --> 00:38:46,180
 To je na internetu, jo?

1221
00:38:46,180 --> 00:38:48,860
 Uzmiješ miš

1222
00:38:48,860 --> 00:38:50,740
 i ne moraš ni kliknut na riječ.

1223
00:38:50,740 --> 00:38:53,060
 Samo nek miš pređe preko,

1224
00:38:53,060 --> 00:38:54,420
 ja ga znam štakor, ne miš.

1225
00:38:54,420 --> 00:38:56,320
 I pređi preko riječ

1226
00:38:56,320 --> 00:38:57,920
 i pojavi se prozorčić

1227
00:38:57,920 --> 00:39:01,160
 i svaka riječ se razrađuje

1228
00:39:01,160 --> 00:39:02,700
 ono nominativ, genativ,

1229
00:39:02,700 --> 00:39:03,720
 množina,

1230
00:39:03,720 --> 00:39:05,600
 ma fantastično nešto.

1231
00:39:05,600 --> 00:39:06,540
 Ja to često korisim

1232
00:39:06,540 --> 00:39:07,140
 za moj vjeru nauk,

1233
00:39:07,140 --> 00:39:07,960
 za propojedi i tako.

1234
00:39:07,960 --> 00:39:09,580
 I ja gledam ovdje,

1235
00:39:09,580 --> 00:39:11,180
 inače pravila hermenutika,

1236
00:39:11,180 --> 00:39:12,820
 kad čitate Bibliju,

1237
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:14,780
 ako se neka riječ ponavlja

1238
00:39:14,780 --> 00:39:15,480
 više puta,

1239
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:16,640
 to je jako važno.

1240
00:39:16,640 --> 00:39:19,140
 Svaka riječ je važna.

1241
00:39:19,140 --> 00:39:20,280
 Ja vidim ono,

1242
00:39:20,280 --> 00:39:21,700
 ljubiš li me,

1243
00:39:21,700 --> 00:39:22,640
 voliš li me,

1244
00:39:22,640 --> 00:39:23,500
 pa znam da te volim.

1245
00:39:23,500 --> 00:39:24,620
 Ono, sedam, osam puta,

1246
00:39:24,620 --> 00:39:25,980
 idem ja to vidim šta je to,

1247
00:39:25,980 --> 00:39:26,980
 šta se tamo događa,

1248
00:39:26,980 --> 00:39:28,020
 kakva je to ljubav.

1249
00:39:28,020 --> 00:39:30,220
 Petar njega pita,

1250
00:39:30,220 --> 00:39:32,180
 Isus njega pita,

1251
00:39:32,180 --> 00:39:33,720
 Petre,

1252
00:39:33,720 --> 00:39:36,140
 jel ti mene agapiraš?

1253
00:39:36,140 --> 00:39:37,780
 Grečka riječ, agape.

1254
00:39:37,780 --> 00:39:40,300
 Agape znači ona ljubav

1255
00:39:40,300 --> 00:39:41,860
 gdje daješ sve do boli

1256
00:39:41,860 --> 00:39:43,180
 i ne tražiš ništa na trak.

1257
00:39:43,180 --> 00:39:44,700
 To znači žrtva,

1258
00:39:44,700 --> 00:39:46,580
 služenje, služenje, služenje.

1259
00:39:46,580 --> 00:39:47,660
 I Petar odgovara,

1260
00:39:47,660 --> 00:39:48,800
 pa ja te filiram,

1261
00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:50,240
 volim te kao prijatelj.

1262
00:39:50,240 --> 00:39:52,440
 Dakle,

1263
00:39:52,440 --> 00:39:54,580
 jel ti Petre mene tako ljubiš

1264
00:39:54,580 --> 00:39:56,260
 da si spreman da život za mene

1265
00:39:56,260 --> 00:39:58,200
 bez uvjeta,

1266
00:39:58,200 --> 00:39:59,000
 bez kriterija.

1267
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:00,320
 Ma, pa, okej si.

1268
00:40:00,320 --> 00:40:04,240
 Dakle, Petar odgovara,

1269
00:40:04,240 --> 00:40:05,360
 filija, ok?

1270
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:06,820
 To je kao prijateljska ljubav.

1271
00:40:06,820 --> 00:40:09,760
 To ti je ljubav koja je uvjetovana.

1272
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:11,460
 Mi smo prijatelji

1273
00:40:11,460 --> 00:40:13,160
 jer igramo nogomet petak večer.

1274
00:40:13,160 --> 00:40:14,760
 To su moji nogometni prijatelji.

1275
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:16,580
 Onda imam moji prijatelji

1276
00:40:16,580 --> 00:40:17,540
 s kimi idem pet sanje.

1277
00:40:17,540 --> 00:40:18,960
 Onda imam kvartovske prijatelji.

1278
00:40:18,960 --> 00:40:20,460
 To je uvjetovano prijateljstvo, jel?

1279
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:22,100
 Što nije loše.

1280
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:24,260
 Ali Isus ga pita,

1281
00:40:24,260 --> 00:40:26,240
 Petre, a ti mene agapiraš?

1282
00:40:26,240 --> 00:40:27,160
 On kaže,

1283
00:40:27,160 --> 00:40:27,960
 volim te ko prijatelja.

1284
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:30,300
 I pita ga drugi puta.

1285
00:40:30,300 --> 00:40:33,260
 Petre, a ti mene agapiraš?

1286
00:40:33,260 --> 00:40:34,960
 On kaže, pa,

1287
00:40:34,960 --> 00:40:35,900
 volim te ko prijatelja.

1288
00:40:35,900 --> 00:40:38,620
 Sad parafriziram prebod, jel?

1289
00:40:38,620 --> 00:40:39,560
 I treći put.

1290
00:40:39,560 --> 00:40:40,740
 Isus kaže,

1291
00:40:40,740 --> 00:40:41,440
 okej, skužim.

1292
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:44,700
 Petre, a ti mene voliš ko prijatelja?

1293
00:40:44,700 --> 00:40:45,820
 Onda Petar kaže,

1294
00:40:45,820 --> 00:40:47,140
 pa Isus, pa rekao sam ti već

1295
00:40:47,140 --> 00:40:48,160
 da volim te ko prijatelja.

1296
00:40:48,160 --> 00:40:51,300
 Dakle, Isus čak spušta kriterij.

1297
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:53,620
 Zašto?

1298
00:40:53,620 --> 00:40:54,540
 Jer nije spreman.

1299
00:40:54,540 --> 00:40:56,560
 Nije spreman.

1300
00:40:56,560 --> 00:40:58,500
 Ovo je fascinantno,

1301
00:40:58,500 --> 00:40:59,140
 Evanđelje.

1302
00:40:59,140 --> 00:41:01,340
 Znači što ovo znači?

1303
00:41:01,340 --> 00:41:03,480
 Da, da gospodin tebe uzme

1304
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:04,680
 onako u toj fazi,

1305
00:41:04,680 --> 00:41:07,520
 nisu svi spremni na sve.

1306
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:10,620
 Znači,

1307
00:41:10,620 --> 00:41:12,260
 neki dan je bila jedna djevojka,

1308
00:41:12,260 --> 00:41:14,740
 ona je se isto nedavno obratila,

1309
00:41:14,740 --> 00:41:16,540
 i sad ona nju muči

1310
00:41:16,540 --> 00:41:19,360
 što ona na faksu

1311
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:20,840
 nije uspjela

1312
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:22,100
 obraćati ljudi

1313
00:41:22,100 --> 00:41:22,820
 i opomenjati.

1314
00:41:22,820 --> 00:41:24,300
 Lako, polako, draga.

1315
00:41:24,300 --> 00:41:26,040
 Ti nisi pozvana na to.

1316
00:41:26,040 --> 00:41:27,680
 Polako.

1317
00:41:27,680 --> 00:41:30,440
 Bog nije despot.

1318
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:33,060
 I obraćenici moji veliki problem s time.

1319
00:41:33,060 --> 00:41:35,340
 Vidite šta Isus ovdje radi.

1320
00:41:35,340 --> 00:41:36,820
 Na kraju, kada on vidi

1321
00:41:36,820 --> 00:41:37,440
 da ne može,

1322
00:41:37,440 --> 00:41:38,640
 ne zna šta je Agape,

1323
00:41:38,640 --> 00:41:40,100
 on kaže, dobro, Petre,

1324
00:41:40,100 --> 00:41:41,400
 ili me voliš ko prijatelja?

1325
00:41:41,400 --> 00:41:42,800
 Rekao, pa naravno da te volim.

1326
00:41:42,800 --> 00:41:43,660
 Pa dobro, najde.

1327
00:41:44,700 --> 00:41:45,620
 Ali ona mu kaže,

1328
00:41:45,620 --> 00:41:46,820
 ali jednog dana,

1329
00:41:46,820 --> 00:41:47,520
 Petre,

1330
00:41:47,520 --> 00:41:49,740
 ićeš kamo ti ne želiš ići.

1331
00:41:49,740 --> 00:41:50,740
 To je Agape.

1332
00:41:50,740 --> 00:41:52,480
 Ali nisi još spreman na to.

1333
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:54,580
 Ok?

1334
00:41:54,580 --> 00:41:57,240
 Bogu faleluja za ovo evanđelje.

1335
00:41:57,240 --> 00:42:01,120
 Jer većina nismo spremni.

1336
00:42:01,120 --> 00:42:04,860
 Vidite kako ta duhovna zrelost je važna.

1337
00:42:04,860 --> 00:42:06,780
 Priznati svoje ograničenje.

1338
00:42:06,780 --> 00:42:09,520
 Petar je već se zaletio,

1339
00:42:09,520 --> 00:42:10,480
 daću život za tebe.

1340
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:11,040
 Ja, right.

1341
00:42:11,040 --> 00:42:13,440
 Daj, Petre, smiri sa čemu.

1342
00:42:13,440 --> 00:42:14,660
 Maj, šuti, šuti.

1343
00:42:14,660 --> 00:42:16,060
 ali,

1344
00:42:16,060 --> 00:42:18,400
 ipak Petar ima to srce.

1345
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:19,420
 Daćeš ti jednog dana.

1346
00:42:19,420 --> 00:42:20,080
 Ne još, Petre.

1347
00:42:20,080 --> 00:42:20,820
 Sam polako.

1348
00:42:20,820 --> 00:42:21,980
 Ok.

1349
00:42:21,980 --> 00:42:23,780
 Ok.

1350
00:42:25,580 --> 00:42:30,100
 I sada, treća faza, ta zadnja,

1351
00:42:30,100 --> 00:42:32,140
 duhovna zrelost.

1352
00:42:32,140 --> 00:42:35,200
 Ja mislim da su mnogi u toj fazi.

1353
00:42:35,200 --> 00:42:37,900
 Ali ja mislim da paralelno mnogi se čistimo.

1354
00:42:38,900 --> 00:42:43,480
 Dakle, što želim reći, ovo nije ono baš kronološki, strogo.

1355
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:47,360
 Ne, ja se čistim još uvijek, ali mogu se prepoznati i u drugoj fazi.

1356
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:59,160
 To je tako zvijek, a to je tako zvijek, a to je tako zvona faza sjedinjenje, a to je nakon silska duha svijetoga, gdje je taj isti Petar, koji je bio tako pun straha, koji je jedna slušknja, kad je rekla bu, on je skočio.

1357
00:42:59,720 --> 00:43:06,140
 Sada, u sili i u snazi, navješta u jeruzalinskim ulicama i tri tišće ljudi se obraćaju.

1358
00:43:06,140 --> 00:43:13,460
 Dovode ga tamo i bićuju ga i on kaže, raduj se Ivane, što možemo trpiti radi imena.

1359
00:43:13,460 --> 00:43:15,100
 Eto.

1360
00:43:15,100 --> 00:43:18,340
 Ali šta se sad događa kod Petra?

1361
00:43:18,340 --> 00:43:25,400
 Prije Petar je bio malo sebićan, pa je tražio svoje, pa nemoj ti na križić, pa ovo, pa ona, pa se malo boji.

1362
00:43:25,400 --> 00:43:33,920
 Ali sada, duhovno očinstvo, sada Petar širi vjeru, sada Petar dovede drugi ljudi do Isusa Hrista.

1363
00:43:33,920 --> 00:43:36,260
 To je pravo krišćanstvo, to je duhovna zrelost.

1364
00:43:36,260 --> 00:43:47,320
 Dakle, prvo se malo on čisti, on nam dođe do jednog ekvilibrija, a on dan prijeđe na evangelizaciju, odnosno dovođenje druge Isusu Hrista.

1365
00:43:47,320 --> 00:43:52,640
 Ako ti nemaš potrebu govoriti o Isu, još ga nisi upoznao.

1366
00:43:53,480 --> 00:43:58,620
 Ako nemaš potrebu govoriti o Isu, ako imaš potrebu govoriti, to još nije dovoljno da govoriš o Njemu.

1367
00:43:58,620 --> 00:44:02,260
 Nima neki ljudi koji ne smiju govoriti o Njemu. Ne još. Ne još.

1368
00:44:02,260 --> 00:44:05,920
 Ali Bogu hvala ako imaš potrebu.

1369
00:44:05,920 --> 00:44:13,300
 Petar je došao u jednu fazu gdje ne samo da govori o Hristu, nego on trpi radi Isusa.

1370
00:44:13,300 --> 00:44:18,360
 On trpi radi Isusa i čini čudesa i tako dalje.

1371
00:44:18,360 --> 00:44:21,880
 To je ta faza dijela apostolski, mi to možemo vidjeti.

1372
00:44:21,880 --> 00:44:24,920
 I ta njegova hrabrost i tako dalje.

1373
00:44:24,920 --> 00:44:27,500
 Engleski se kaže boldness.

1374
00:44:27,500 --> 00:44:31,900
 On navješta u sili i u snazi.

1375
00:44:36,520 --> 00:44:38,480
 Evo, na kraju, suma sumarum.

1376
00:44:38,480 --> 00:44:49,640
 Kajanje, stjecanje, znanje, poniznost.

1377
00:44:54,280 --> 00:45:00,720
 I nakon pada dizanje, ja mogu samo misliti kako je bilo Petru kad je zatajio Isusa.

1378
00:45:00,720 --> 00:45:01,700
 To je tako teško.

1379
00:45:01,700 --> 00:45:03,560
 Znate što vidim kod mnogih ljudi.

1380
00:45:03,560 --> 00:45:05,460
 Dožive poraz.

1381
00:45:05,460 --> 00:45:07,840
 Padnu u težak grijeh.

1382
00:45:07,840 --> 00:45:11,420
 Mnogi svećenici mi dolaze na ispovjed.

1383
00:45:11,420 --> 00:45:15,460
 I on taj svećenik isti koji padne u težak nekih grijeh.

1384
00:45:15,460 --> 00:45:17,560
 Tako on...

1385
00:45:17,560 --> 00:45:19,380
 Pazi u koju džavosku zamku on pada.

1386
00:45:19,380 --> 00:45:25,060
 Sad on kaže, e nisam dostojan sad govoriti jer sam ja dvoličnik jer sam ja pa...

1387
00:45:25,060 --> 00:45:25,340
 Sad ću...

1388
00:45:25,340 --> 00:45:26,520
 Ne budalo, šuti.

1389
00:45:26,520 --> 00:45:31,040
 Ne, ti moraš govoriti zato što ti nisi garantor ove istine.

1390
00:45:31,040 --> 00:45:34,720
 Ti jesi dvoličnik ukoliko ne živiš ono što propovjedaš.

1391
00:45:34,720 --> 00:45:38,320
 Ali prijatelju dragi, ti si pozvan na vještati i dizati se.

1392
00:45:38,320 --> 00:45:40,480
 Jer šta džavao radi nakon pada?

1393
00:45:40,480 --> 00:45:42,580
 Skačeti na glavu i kao vi šta si napravio.

1394
00:45:42,580 --> 00:45:44,040
 A šta radi prije pada?

1395
00:45:44,040 --> 00:45:46,040
 Padni, padni, griješi, griješi.

1396
00:45:46,040 --> 00:45:48,440
 A nakon pada, eto vidi šta si napravio.

1397
00:45:48,700 --> 00:45:50,660
 Krivnja nakon ispovjedne dolazi od Boga.

1398
00:45:50,660 --> 00:45:56,560
 Zato ja vidim kod obračenike i kod nas kršćana, mladi katolici,

1399
00:45:56,560 --> 00:45:59,600
 to da žare, žare, žare.

1400
00:45:59,600 --> 00:46:01,980
 I onda padnu i onda ništa.

1401
00:46:01,980 --> 00:46:02,840
 Nema ga više nigdje.

1402
00:46:02,840 --> 00:46:05,820
 I još jedan savjet, molim vas.

1403
00:46:05,820 --> 00:46:08,880
 Ja sam skruvao jedan termin, a to su posvuduše.

1404
00:46:11,680 --> 00:46:13,040
 Znate šta su posvuduše?

1405
00:46:13,040 --> 00:46:15,540
 Ja vidim da neki znaju.

1406
00:46:15,540 --> 00:46:19,460
 To znači ponedljak večer sam u Skacu,

1407
00:46:19,460 --> 00:46:22,180
 a utorak večer sam kod, ne znam,

1408
00:46:22,180 --> 00:46:24,320
 na novo sredu sam kod Don Damira,

1409
00:46:24,320 --> 00:46:26,600
 četvrtak sam i tako dalje.

1410
00:46:26,600 --> 00:46:27,140
 Gledajte.

1411
00:46:27,140 --> 00:46:30,040
 To je dobro, ima vrijeme i za to.

1412
00:46:30,040 --> 00:46:31,420
 Malo duhovni šoping.

1413
00:46:33,420 --> 00:46:34,100
 Pa je.

1414
00:46:34,100 --> 00:46:38,020
 Ali znate šta je znak duhovne zrelosti?

1415
00:46:38,020 --> 00:46:39,920
 Posvećenje.

1416
00:46:39,920 --> 00:46:42,600
 Posvećenje negdje.

1417
00:46:42,600 --> 00:46:45,760
 Znate šta je meni najgore?

1418
00:46:45,760 --> 00:46:48,320
 Kada meni neko dođe i pita me za savjet.

1419
00:46:48,320 --> 00:46:50,660
 Momak, djevojka.

1420
00:46:50,660 --> 00:46:52,880
 Ali Ramos mi je rekao,

1421
00:46:52,880 --> 00:46:53,780
 znači šta, izađe.

1422
00:46:53,780 --> 00:46:55,440
 Izađe.

1423
00:46:55,440 --> 00:46:57,840
 Dakle, šta ta osoba radi?

1424
00:46:57,840 --> 00:47:01,380
 Ide kod Ramosa

1425
00:47:01,380 --> 00:47:03,440
 i pokupi ono što želi.

1426
00:47:03,440 --> 00:47:07,000
 Ide ondan, dođe kod Don Damira,

1427
00:47:07,000 --> 00:47:08,580
 pokupi ono što želi.

1428
00:47:08,580 --> 00:47:11,100
 Ondan će možda ići,

1429
00:47:11,100 --> 00:47:12,000
 evo, Paterike odšla,

1430
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:13,260
 ode malo kod Paterike,

1431
00:47:13,260 --> 00:47:14,740
 pokupiš,

1432
00:47:14,740 --> 00:47:17,120
 onda ide kod ovoga fratra na Kapitolu

1433
00:47:17,120 --> 00:47:17,840
 i tako dalje.

1434
00:47:17,840 --> 00:47:20,160
 To je tako nezrelo.

1435
00:47:20,160 --> 00:47:22,000
 Znate kako je to nezrelo?

1436
00:47:22,000 --> 00:47:24,220
 Ja kad skužim da se to događa,

1437
00:47:24,220 --> 00:47:25,660
 ja odmah prekidam razgor,

1438
00:47:25,660 --> 00:47:26,460
 izađi iz Mugurga.

1439
00:47:26,460 --> 00:47:28,420
 Mislim, ne moraš izaći iz Mugurga,

1440
00:47:28,420 --> 00:47:29,440
 ali nećemo pričati više o ovom,

1441
00:47:29,440 --> 00:47:31,280
 možemo pričati o sportu,

1442
00:47:31,380 --> 00:47:32,880
 politici, o izborima i tako dalje.

1443
00:47:32,880 --> 00:47:34,080
 Evo, ali nećemo ovo.

1444
00:47:34,080 --> 00:47:36,580
 To je duhovno nezrelo.

1445
00:47:36,580 --> 00:47:38,980
 Zato dobro je naći duhovnika

1446
00:47:38,980 --> 00:47:39,900
 i drža se njega.

1447
00:47:39,900 --> 00:47:41,980
 A mijenjanje ispovjednika?

1448
00:47:41,980 --> 00:47:50,580
 Mijenjanje ispovjednika?

1449
00:47:50,580 --> 00:47:53,080
 Nemu ja nemu sve reći.

1450
00:47:53,080 --> 00:47:56,380
 Ja njemu ovo reći.

1451
00:47:56,380 --> 00:47:59,180
 Pa ići kod onoga i tako dalje.

1452
00:47:59,180 --> 00:48:01,000
 Jeste čuli za onoga lika?

1453
00:48:01,000 --> 00:48:04,080
 Četardeset godina se nije ispovjedio.

1454
00:48:04,080 --> 00:48:05,260
 Ono varo ženu,

1455
00:48:05,260 --> 00:48:06,620
 nagovoro ženu na pobačaj.

1456
00:48:06,620 --> 00:48:08,800
 Krao od radnike,

1457
00:48:08,800 --> 00:48:09,660
 ovo ono,

1458
00:48:09,660 --> 00:48:11,280
 došao kod svećenika,

1459
00:48:11,280 --> 00:48:11,960
 ispovjedio se.

1460
00:48:11,960 --> 00:48:13,340
 I ono svećenika je kao,

1461
00:48:13,340 --> 00:48:14,360
 Bogu, hvala četardeset godina.

1462
00:48:14,360 --> 00:48:15,300
 Ona je pokora.

1463
00:48:15,300 --> 00:48:16,840
 Rekao, ok, priznaj sve ženi.

1464
00:48:17,620 --> 00:48:18,600
 I pokora mu je bilo,

1465
00:48:18,600 --> 00:48:20,640
 ajme, meni, vrati novce koliko je moguće.

1466
00:48:20,640 --> 00:48:22,220
 Mislim, skoro nemoguće,

1467
00:48:22,220 --> 00:48:24,380
 ali mora napraviti reparaciju za to.

1468
00:48:24,380 --> 00:48:26,340
 I ovaj izlađe iz ispovjednika,

1469
00:48:26,340 --> 00:48:27,080
 dobio od rješenja,

1470
00:48:27,080 --> 00:48:28,920
 ajme, meni, kako će ovu pokoru napraviti?

1471
00:48:28,920 --> 00:48:29,660
 Znaš šta je napraviti?

1472
00:48:29,660 --> 00:48:31,060
 Za dva tjedna išao opet na ispovjed

1473
00:48:31,060 --> 00:48:31,780
 i prvi grijeh,

1474
00:48:31,780 --> 00:48:33,800
 nisam izvršio zadnju pokoru.

1475
00:48:33,800 --> 00:48:35,140
 I ovaj mu kaže,

1476
00:48:35,140 --> 00:48:35,840
 jedan od če je naš.

1477
00:48:42,840 --> 00:48:44,580
 Bože, sada je snačno ljudima dao ideju.

1478
00:48:44,580 --> 00:48:48,240
 Ok, ali gledajte,

1479
00:48:48,240 --> 00:48:50,060
 ovo je anegdota.

1480
00:48:50,060 --> 00:48:53,620
 Ali to je znak,

1481
00:48:53,620 --> 00:48:56,200
 stvari što se događa kod nekih ljudi,

1482
00:48:56,200 --> 00:48:57,960
 što ja vidim u duhovnoj sceni,

1483
00:48:57,960 --> 00:48:58,520
 u Zagrebu,

1484
00:48:58,520 --> 00:48:59,820
 duhovna nezrelost.

1485
00:48:59,820 --> 00:49:02,780
 Mjenjanje duhovnika,

1486
00:49:02,780 --> 00:49:04,400
 mijenjanje ispovjednika,

1487
00:49:04,400 --> 00:49:06,660
 i doslovce duhovni šoping.

1488
00:49:06,660 --> 00:49:08,200
 Dakle, ideš ovdje za to,

1489
00:49:08,200 --> 00:49:09,620
 aha, ja znam kakav je on.

1490
00:49:09,620 --> 00:49:12,720
 I tako, ne, ne, drži se, jedno.

1491
00:49:13,560 --> 00:49:14,520
 Drži se, jedno.

1492
00:49:14,520 --> 00:49:16,840
 I to vrijedi za karizmu,

1493
00:49:16,840 --> 00:49:18,280
 odnosno za duhovnost.

1494
00:49:18,280 --> 00:49:20,200
 Bogu fala,

1495
00:49:20,200 --> 00:49:21,980
 crkva je tako bogata.

1496
00:49:21,980 --> 00:49:24,860
 Franjevačka,

1497
00:49:24,860 --> 00:49:25,620
 Isusovačka,

